Yang Haodong preached the spirit of the Sixth Plenary Session of the 19th  Central Committee of the CPC and the congress of Party representatives.
Draw energy from the history of struggle of the Party of 100 hundred years
Message of Hunan Daily on December 10 (full-media journaly: Gong Bowei), according to unified arrangement of the provincial Party committee, in the morning of December 10, Yang Haodong, a member of the Standing Committee of CPC Provincial Committee and the minister of Propaganda Department of the provincial Party committee, preached in the Malan Mountain video cultural and creative park, to study the spirit of the sixth plenary session of the 19th central committee and the spirit of the important instructions about Hunan by General Secretary Xi Jinping, and the spirit of the 12th Party congress of Hunan.
In combination of feelings and experiences, Yang Haodong interpreted the core essence and the requirement on practice of the spirit of the sixth plenary session of the 19th central committee on three aspects, i.e., original intention & mission, self-revolution & the young Party, and leaders and theory of the Party.
As pointed by Yang Haodong, it is necessary to combine the spirit of the spirit of the sixth plenary session of the 19th central committee and the spirit of the important instructions about Hunan by General Secretary Xi Jinping, and the spirit of the 12th Party congress of Hunan, to digest them and strengthen the guarding of the “two-establishment” and the “two-guarding”, so as to make progress as guided by General Secretary Xi Jinping.
In the interaction and exchange link, representatives of grass-rooted cadres, representatives of enterprises and representatives of young people asked questions about relationship among the three historical resolutions, correct understanding on decisive significance of the “two-establishment”, the way for cultural enterprises to master the orientation and the way for young people to abstract energy from the Party’s history of 100 years; Yang Haodong answered the questions with popular language and vivid cases, and he wished the young Party members to abstract energy for progress from the history of the Party of 100 years and unified around the Party Central Committee and followed the decisions made by the Party, to write responsibility and undertaking with youth and contributions.